# Chat Frontend — Next.js 16 App Router

## Tech Stack

- **Next.js 16** (App Router, React 19, `use()` for async params)
- **Tailwind CSS v4** with `@theme` in `globals.css`
- **Zustand** for client state (auth, chat UI)
- **TanStack React Query v5** for server state
- **Socket.IO client** for realtime (namespace `/chat`)
- **react-hook-form + zod** for forms
- **lucide-react** for icons
- **axios** with auth interceptor and retry

## Directory Layout

```
app/
  layout.tsx          # Root: Thai font (Noto Sans Thai), QueryProvider
  page.tsx            # Server redirect → /chat
  login/page.tsx      # Login (client component)
  chat/
    layout.tsx        # AuthProvider + Sidebar + useSocket
    page.tsx          # "Select a room" empty state
    [roomId]/page.tsx # ChatWindow (use() to unwrap params Promise)
components/
  chat/    # ChatBubble, ChatInput, ChatWindow, RoomItem, Sidebar, TypingIndicator
  layout/  # AdminProfile
  ui/      # Avatar, Badge, Button, Input, PlatformIcon, Spinner
hooks/     # useAuth, useMessages, useRooms, useSocket
lib/       # axios instance, socket singleton, cn(), error-codes
providers/ # AuthProvider (route guard), QueryProvider
stores/    # auth.store (persisted), chat.store
schemas/   # zod schemas for forms
types/     # TypeScript interfaces (Room, Chat, Platform, User, etc.)
```

## State Architecture

- **auth.store** (Zustand persist): token, userId, username, role, activeShopId
- **chat.store** (Zustand): activeRoomId, platformFilter, typingUsers
- **React Query keys**: `['rooms', platformId]`, `['messages', roomId]`, `['shops']`

## API Layer

- Base URL: `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` (default `http://localhost:5000`)
- Auto Bearer token from Zustand persist storage
- 401 → clear storage → redirect `/login`
- Retry: 3 attempts with exponential backoff for 5xx/network errors

## Socket Events (namespace `/chat`)

- `new_message` → merge into React Query messages cache + invalidate rooms
- `room_updated` → patch rooms cache
- `typing` → update Zustand typingUsers
- `messages_read` → invalidate messages cache

## Realtime Flow

```
ChatLayout mounts → useSocket() connects
  → ChatWindow mounts → joinRoom(roomId)
  → new_message event → update query cache
  → ChatWindow unmounts → leaveRoom(roomId)
```

## Backend API Endpoints Used

| Hook/Component | Method | Endpoint |
|----------------|--------|----------|
| useLogin | POST | /auth/login |
| useRooms | GET | /rooms |
| useShops | GET | /shops |
| useMessages | GET | /chats/room/{roomId}/detailed |
| ChatInput | POST | /chats/send |

## Supported Message Types

ChatMessageType: `TEXT`, `IMAGE`, `VIDEO`, `AUDIO`, `FILE`
PlatformType: `LINE`, `FACEBOOK`, `INSTAGRAM`, `SHOPEE`, `LAZADA`
